      <%while ( fontSize <= 3){ %>
         <font color = "green" size = "<%= fontSize %>">
            JSP Tutorial
         </font><br />
         <%fontSize++;%>
      <%}%>
   </body> 
</html> 
 The above code will generate the following result ? 

   JSP Tutorial



